{"tid":1784814,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"老老豆豆 黑警先最唔想運動收皮 因為平靜落黎佢地就無利用價值","createTime":"2019-12-16T03:01:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-16T05:11:14.000Z","uid":39092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c2a82418b90ee44f288c8942619809d082bfdcaf","tid":1784814,"uid":39092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T03:01:32.000Z","msg":"班撚屌而家想玩集體負責<br />\n只要仲有少少「亂」，佢地就仲有價值唔洗做condom<br />\n係人都知要想平呢個局最簡單就好似乾隆留返和珅一樣 （讀下歷史啦毅進仔）<br />\n呢班19 condom 仔比人割只係遲早既事<br />\n班撚屌尋晚就同你炒返熱佢<br />\n反正一日仲有「亂」，<br />\n做野唔洗上身 （唔係覺得佢地會諗到咁長遠，呢班正宗腦殘淨係諗到眼前利益）<br />\n又要有OT錢 仲可以扮到高人一等咁樣自我感覺良好<br />\n而家點叫停班狗 根本唔受控制<br />\n<br />\n呢一點係港共同支聯辦欺上暪下再唔正視<br />\n香港只會加速攬炒<br />\n維尼一定好快收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e34b6114eccf66cce4aa2b68d78ab8e549bbc22","tid":1784814,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T05:11:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽晚7點愛丁堡見</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">哀悼香港人道災難</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PY03AQa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPY03AQa.jpg&h=511bc04b&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}